      <title>人民币投资者紧张不安，因中国假期可能引发波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/yuan-investors-on-edge-as-china-s-holiday-may-spur-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国明显暂缓受到美国更严厉的关税影响，但投资者仍然对人民币持怀疑态度，担心在即将到来的为期一周的交易假期期间及之后可能出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/yuan-investors-on-edge-as-china-s-holiday-may-spur-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
